{"type":"message","id":"695ea47d","parentId":"89374469","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:31.760Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759271759}}
{"type":"message","id":"f24bba14","parentId":"695ea47d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:34.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1) is asking me (@_all, but I'm the one mentioned/active) to read and understand MD files in my workspace, introduce myself, explain my work responsibilities, and show my understanding of the company's business.\n\nLet me read through my relevant files to give a comprehensive introduction. I already have IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, USER.md, AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md, and TOOLS.md from the startup context. Let me also check if there are any other MD files or SOPs I should be aware of.\n\n\nI've got the key content loaded from my identity files and memory documentation, so I can now compose a response that introduces who I am as 8号机动虾, outlines my role as a flexible support system across all teams, and demonstrates how I understand the company's operations.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_23db27fdc5564bd2a37cd35c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp -name \"*.md\" -not -path \"*/node_modules/*\" | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20699,"output":460,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21159,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759271760,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b1f56905-4b7b-9914-b062-12debad39c1f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b39dcc5","parentId":"f24bba14","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:34.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_23db27fdc5564bd2a37cd35c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/IDENTITY.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/HEARTBEAT.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/MEMORY.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/BOOTSTRAP.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/USER.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/SOUL.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/AGENTS.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/TOOLS.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/IDENTITY.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/HEARTBEAT.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/MEMORY.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/BOOTSTRAP.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/USER.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/SOUL.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/AGENTS.md\n/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp/TOOLS.md","cwd":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/all_round_support_shrimp"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776759274344}}
{"type":"message","id":"85a3d6a3","parentId":"7b39dcc5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:39.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to understand the MD files, introduce myself, explain my responsibilities and understanding of the company business. Let me compose a response based on what I've already read from my workspace files.\n\nI already have all the file contents loaded in the project context. Let me compose a natural response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是 **8号机动虾** 🦐\n\n先说我是谁——\n\n我是一只\"机动应急打杂虾\"。公司里一共有12张权限卡，从0号老板到7号数据虾各有明确分工，而我就是那个**兜底和补位**的角色。简单说就三句话：哪里需要去哪里、没人干的我来干、到期没完成的我去催。\n\n---\n\n**我的职责分三层：**\n\n**第一层 · 我做主（自主行动）**\n- 日常替补其他岗位做简单工作\n- 日程提醒、待办检查\n- 杂事处理、物资管理\n- 监督全公司任务系统的完成情况\n\n**第二层 · 我报备（做完再报告）**\n- 代替其他岗位干活超过24小时\n- 发现公司级流程漏洞并修复\n\n**第三层 · 问老板（需要指令才能动）**\n- 接手从没碰过的突发高难任务\n- 动用备用资金超过300元\n- 处理涉及法律风险的状况\n\n---\n\n**对公司业务的理解：**\n\n我们是一家资质代办类公司，业务链条比较完整：\n\n1. **前端获客** → 品牌虾做展示引流，短视频虾拍内容，私域虾做运营维护\n2. **中端转化** → 销售虾（标准/大客户）承接线索、报价签约\n3. **后端交付** → 代办虾（标准/大客户）按SOP执行具体代办流程\n4. **售后维系** → 售后虾做回访、转介绍、投诉处理\n5. **数据支撑** → 数据虾做统计分析和仪表盘\n\n这个链路里最容易出问题的环节恰恰是我该关注的——比如销售签了单但代办虾没及时跟上、或者某条产品线连续逾期没人管。我就是那个**盯着全链路不掉链子**的人。\n\n每轮我会把所有岗位的SOP学一遍，确保替补的时候不至于帮倒忙。有任务逾期了我直接找责任人催，催不动就上报给老板。\n\n---\n\n以上就是我的自我介绍 👆 有啥需要随时叫我就行 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21119,"output":574,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759274346,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8974992d-d5da-9953-9fba-40478d4d532e"}}
